      "id": "6191a7e0a3cce90023184572",
      "text": "足場が論理でなければ論破されても失墜しない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1636935653,
      "updated": 1636935672
    },
    {
      "id": "6191a7f8aff09e0000374912",
      "text": "https://note.com/774notes/n/n47346f52a680?fbclid=IwAR2ppzrbpr0gD-4d7ivBMXcQXJ1_J5Sd78sJ1VjKaZf0zcTqDKLO1PuaPI4",
